Package: shinyglass
Type: Package
Title: Apple-Inspired Liquid Glass Design for Shiny Applications
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person("Eric", "Anderson", role = c("aut", "cre"), email = "eric.ray.anderson@gmail.com")
Description: Provides the exported function 'glass_theme()', which returns a
    'bslib' theme object styled with an Apple-inspired Liquid Glass
    aesthetic for use in 'shiny' applications. The theme applies
    translucent surfaces, backdrop blur, and system typography to
    Bootstrap components. See Apple's Liquid Glass design overview at
    <https://developer.apple.com/documentation/technologyoverviews/liquid-glass>.
